### 10. Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Mega-prompt too complex, quality drops | Medium | Condense system prompt; if quality is unacceptable, fall back to parallel 6-call strategy (`Promise.all`) |
| Output exceeds token limit | Low | Gemini 2.5 Flash supports 65K output tokens; our ~8K estimate is well within limits |
| localStorage quota exceeded | Medium | Pre-generated cache adds ~30-50KB per analysis. Add a cleanup function that removes cache for analyses older than 30 days |
| Race condition: user generates before mega completes | Low | Check `megaGenerationStatus` on tool page; if generating, show indicator but allow manual generation; if manual result exists when mega completes, do not overwrite |
| Gemini API rate limits | Low | Single additional call per analysis. Current architecture already makes multiple calls. |

